                                "textData": {
                                    "text": "Gangakalyana is the Flag Ship Programme of Govt. of Karnataka developed a “Mobile App” \"Gangakalyana\" which facilitate unit officers, stake holders to document and update the various stages of the implementation. The app established harmonic linkage between Head Office, District Office, Borewell Agencies, Pumpset Suppliers, ESCOMS and beneficiary for seamless communication and co-ordination. ",
                                    "decorations": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "BOLD",
                                            "fontWeightValue": 700
